<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Server Error</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #e74c3c;
            margin: 0;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #333;
        }

        a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #3498db;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

            a:hover {
                background-color: #2980b9;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>500 - Server Error</h1>
        <p>Sorry, something went wrong on our end. We're working to fix it as soon as possible.</p>
        <a href="/Customer/Index">Go to Homepage</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
